article.description: — DeVante’ Jones had a career-high 35 points as Coastal Carolina romped past Alice Lloyd College 86-63 on Friday night.
article.headline: Coastal Carolina beats Alice Lloyd College 86-63
article.linkText: Coastal Carolina beats Alice Lloyd College 86-63
article.story: CONWAY, S.C. -- — DeVante’ Jones had a career-high 35 points as Coastal Carolina romped past Alice Lloyd College 86-63 on Friday night. Jones made 14 of 18 shots, including 4 of 6 on 3-pointers. He added five steals. Deanthony Tipler had 12 points for Coastal Carolina (6-1), which earned its sixth straight home victory. Essam Mostafa added 12 points and 15 rebounds. Ebrima Dibba had six rebounds. Bryce Slone had 13 points for the Eagles. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
